* ============================================================
* Sky130 Process Design Kit - Simplified SPICE Models for LTSpice
* Based on SkyWater SKY130 PDK (public, open-source)
* https://github.com/google/skywater-pdk
*
* These are representative BSIM3v3 models derived from the
* publicly available Sky130 corner models.
* TT = Typical-Typical corner
* FF = Fast-Fast corner  
* SS = Slow-Slow corner
* ============================================================

